"""
LogicScale Neural Engine v4.0
world_learner.py — The global learning module.
                   Collects arguments from public sources (Reddit, Bundestag,
                   debate transcripts) and updates global_weights.json
                   so ALL users benefit from real-world patterns.

Sources:
  - Reddit r/ChangeMyView (labeled: delta = "this convinced me")
  - Bundestag Open Data API (parliamentary debates)
  - X/Twitter via API v2 (trending debate topics)
  - Custom debate transcript folder (manual upload)

Run nightly:
    python world_learner.py --source reddit --limit 200
    python world_learner.py --source bundestag --date 2026-04-01
    python world_learner.py --summarize   (update global_weights.json)
"""

